        Constructor for SET_PERSONAL_INFO request. Currently ignores and disables alarms, and sets BT auto timeout to 10 minutes.
        Parameters:
        device - communications target.
        timeout - relative time after operation begins before request is abandoned.
        gender - either MALE or FEMALE (see static members).
        height_cm - height measurement(cm).
        weight_kg - weight measurement(cm).
        stride_cm - stride measurement(cm).
        running_stride_cm - running stride measurement(cm).
